text: Billlie (; stylized as Bi11lie or Billlǃə) is a South Korean girl group made by Mystic Story. Billlie let out their first song on November 10, 2021. The group has seven members: Moon Sua, Suhyeon, Haram, Tsuki, Siyoon, Haruna, and Sheon. == References == Category:2020s South Korean music groups Category:2021 establishments in South Korea Category:K-pop music groups Category:Musical groups established in 2021 Category:South Korean girl groups
